            RecoverySteps: ["Ensure the predicate is a boolean expression", "Add a comparison operator if the expression resolves to a non-boolean type"],
            ExampleBefore: "precept Example\nfield Items as set of number\nrule any i in Items (i + 1) because \"check\"",
            ExampleAfter: "precept Example\nfield Items as set of number\nrule any i in Items (i > 0) because \"has positive\""),

        // ── NameBinder ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
        DiagnosticCode.UndeclaredArg => new(
            nameof(DiagnosticCode.UndeclaredArg),
